<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_personalising_booking_in_stock_with_the_plentymarkets_app">7.2. Personalising booking in stock with the plentymarkets app</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Users can personalise the booing in process using the plentymarkets app settings.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Personalising booking in stock with the plentymarkets app:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Log into the plentymarkets App.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>In the menu bar, tap the <strong>menu symbol</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap <strong>Settings</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap <strong>Incoming items</strong>.<br>
→ The settings menu <strong>Incoming items</strong> opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
